<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Festa del Papà</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1020;
      --bg-soft: #151a2b;
      --accent: #f2c14f;
      --accent-soft: #f7d889;
      --text-main: #f7f4ec;
      --text-soft: #c9c5bb;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --radius: 16px;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      --transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1b2340 0, #050712 55%, #020308 100%);
      color: var(--text-main);
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(10, 14, 30, 0.96), rgba(8, 10, 22, 0.98));
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.12);
      position: relative;
      isolation: isolate;
    }

    .page::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -40%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.12), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0%, rgba(111, 178, 255, 0.12), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    header {
      padding: 40px 32px 32px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    header::after {
      content: "Festa del Papà";
      position: absolute;
      right: -40px;
      bottom: -10px;
      font-size: 64px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      pointer-events: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hero-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .hero-tag span.dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.9);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      margin-top: 10px;
      max-width: 520px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition), background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #ffdf8a);
      color: #2b2108;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.45);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      color: var(--text-main);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .hero-badge {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .hero-badge span.icon {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 0%, #ffffff, #f2c14f);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #2b2108;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.7);
    }

    main {
      padding: 24px 32px 32px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    section {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.06), transparent 55%), var(--bg-soft);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 20px 20px 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    section::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03), transparent 40%);
      opacity: 0.7;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    section > * {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }

    .message-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-main);
      margin-top: 6px;
      white-space: pre-line;
    }

    .message-sign {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .photo-card {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #2a3558, #151a2b);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      min-height: 120px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 10px;
      cursor: default;
      transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition), border-color var(--transition), background var(--transition);
    }

    .photo-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .photo-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      border-color: rgba(242, 193, 79, 0.6);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #36426a, #151a2b);
    }

    .photo-label {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .photo-tag {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      left: 10px;
      z-index: 1;
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }

    .photo-1 {
      background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/3770580/pexels-photo-3770580.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .photo-2 {
      background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/1648374/pexels-photo-1648374.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .photo-3 {
      background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/3770581/pexels-photo-3770581.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .photo-4 {
      background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/3770595/pexels-photo-3770595.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .photo-5 {
      background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/3770594/pexels-photo-3770594.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .photo-6 {
      background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/3770590/pexels-photo-3770590.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .surprise-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .card-soft {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 14px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .card-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .pill {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      color: var(--text-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 18px 32px 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-soft);
    }

    .footer-name {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .footer-note {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }

    .footer-heart {
      color: var(--accent-soft);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      header {
        padding: 28px 20px 22px;
      }

      main {
        padding: 18px 20px 22px;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 14px 20px 18px;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .surprise-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-top {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .hero-badge {
        align-self: flex-start;
      }
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <div class="hero-top">
        <div>
          <div class="hero-tag">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            FESTA DEL PAPÀ • OGGI È IL TUO GIORNO
          </div>
          <h1 class="hero-title">Buona Festa del Papà</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Oggi celebriamo la tua forza, la tua gentilezza e tutto ciò che fai senza chiedere nulla in cambio.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="#messaggio" class="btn btn-primary">
              <span>Leggi il mio messaggio</span>
              <span>↘</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#ricordi" class="btn btn-ghost">
              <span>Guarda i ricordi</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="icon">★</span>
          Un piccolo spazio digitale solo per te, papà.
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="messaggio">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Messaggio per te</h2>
          <div class="section-subtitle">Dal cuore, senza filtri</div>
        </div>
        <p class="message-text">
Papà, non servono grandi parole per dirti quanto sei importante.
Ogni tuo gesto, ogni tuo consiglio, ogni sorriso che mi hai regalato
ha costruito una parte di ciò che sono oggi.

Grazie per esserci sempre, anche quando non lo dico abbastanza.
Oggi è la tua festa, ma la verità è che per me
ogni giorno è un po’ la Festa del Papà, perché ti porto con me
in tutto ciò che faccio.
        </p>
        <div class="message-sign">
          Con affetto,<br />
          <strong>[Il tuo nome]</strong>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="ricordi">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Galleria dei ricordi</h2>
          <div class="section-subtitle">Momenti che porto con me</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
          <div class="photo-card photo-1">
            <div class="photo-tag">Noi due</div>
            <div class="photo-label">Un momento solo nostro</div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-card photo-2">
            <div class="photo-tag">Sorrisi</div>
            <div class="photo-label">Un sorriso che non dimentico</div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-card photo-3">
            <div class="photo-tag">Insieme</div>
            <div class="photo-label">Una giornata semplice, ma speciale</div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-card photo-4">
            <div class="photo-tag">Famiglia</div>
            <div class="photo-label">Il calore di casa con te</div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-card photo-5">
            <div class="photo-tag">Ricordo</div>
            <div class="photo-label">Un abbraccio che vale più di mille parole</div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-card photo-6">
            <div class="photo-tag">Cuore</div>
            <div class="photo-label">Un istante che porto sempre con me</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="sorpresa">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Una sorpresa per te</h2>
          <div class="section-subtitle">Un piccolo regalo digitale</div>
        </div>
        <div class="surprise-layout">
          <div class="card-soft">
            <div class="card-title">Una lettera solo per te</div>
            <div class="card-text">
              Ho raccolto in una lettera quello che a volte faccio fatica a dire a voce.
              Puoi leggerla con calma, quando vuoi, sapendo che ogni parola viene dal cuore.
            </div>
            <div class="pill-row">
              <span class="pill">Gratitudine</span>
              <span class="pill">Ricordi</span>
              <span class="pill">Cuore</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-soft">
            <div class="card-title">La nostra colonna sonora</div>
            <div class="card-text">
              Ho preparato anche una playlist con canzoni che mi fanno pensare a te,
              ai viaggi, alle risate e ai momenti in cui bastava uno sguardo per capirci.
            </div>
            <div class="pill-row">
              <span class="pill">Playlist</span>
              <span class="pill">Ricordi</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div>
        <div class="footer-note">Creato per la Festa del Papà</div>
        <div class="footer-name">Con affetto, [Il tuo nome]</div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-heart">♥</div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
